{
  "stem": "18637.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 454.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I-- when I was freed, I wasn't religious.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I looked for a-- I looked for kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to-- I brought up the kids, they should be-- they should have kosher homes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the forest, whatever you got, you cooked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you-- you never looked at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know once.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew it Yom Kippur, so we didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the guys baked some potatoes was said, it's ready.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, you know what, I wasn't hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But other times, I didn't know what it what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, there, you-- you don't keep religion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You find even a piece of-- anything you find, you eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was your survival.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And sure, you-- you weren't religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But yet, when you're free, you can't go away from it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And when we came to Rowne, I find my sister and my brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were there a year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rowne was free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they used to bomb-- put bombs on the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at night-- at night, they used to put the bombs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So at night, we used to go out from the city, sleep outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they-- a few of them got killed in the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the daytime, we used to return to the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Rowne, I didn't work, but my brother worked.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- he's handy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He fixed shoes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He did all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But probably, by that time, they gave out some food to those people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly how it were, but we weren't hungry already, being in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one helped each other, a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was no Jews left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no-- no-- no--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That survived?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- you have a good feeling for those who were good.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
